MATHLIB Function Reference

Single Precision

This section provides a description of the functions that are single precision.

Single Precision Functions

The routines included in the Math library are provided as both single- and double-precision versions. SP is used to identify the single-precision functions.

  • Acoshsp
  • Acossp
  • Asinhsp
  • Asinsp
  • Atan2sp
  • Atanhsp
  • Atansp
  • Coshsp
  • Cossp
  • Divsp
  • Exp10sp
  • Exp2sp
  • Expsp
  • Log10sp
  • Log2sp
  • Logsp
  • Powsp
  • Recipsp
  • Rsqrtsp
  • Sinhsp
  • Sinsp
  • Sqrtsp
  • Tanhdp
  • Tandp
